Package entities

Class ItemInOrder

java.lang.Object
entities.Item
entities.ItemInOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ItemInOrder extends Item
This class represents an item in an order with additional customization options. It extends the Item class and includes attributes for size, doneness degree, and restrictions.

      Constructs an ItemInOrder with specified details and customizations.
      Parameters:
      itemID - the item id
      supplierID - The unique identifier for the supplier of the item.
      name - The name of the item.
      type - The category of the item, represented by an instance of Category.
      description - A brief description of the item.
      customSize - A boolean indicating whether the item has a custom size option.
      customDonenessDegree - A boolean indicating whether the item has a custom doneness degree option.
      customRestrictions - A boolean indicating whether the item has custom restrictions.
      size - The size of the item if customization is allowed.
      donenessDegree - The doneness degree of the item if customization is allowed.
      restrictions - Any restrictions applied to the item if customization is allowed.
      price - The price of the item.
